The Keys to Your Heart

You are attracted to those who have a split personality - cold as ice on the outside but hot as fire in the heart.
In love, you feel the most alive when everything is uncertain, one moment heaven... the next moment hell.
You'd like to your lover to think you are stylish and alluring.
You would be forced to break up with someone who was ruthless, cold-blooded, and sarcastic.
Your ideal relationship is lasting. You want a relationship that looks to the future... one you can grow with.
Your risk of cheating is zero. You care about society and morality. You would never break a commitment.
You think of marriage as something precious. You'll treasure marriage and treat it as sacred.
In this moment, you think of love as something you thirst for. You'll do anything for love, but you won't fall for it easily.
What Are The Keys To Your Heart?

hey everyone... last night rocked... I had sooo much fun. Me rachel craig n my bro got to the crawfish boil at about 4:30 n we didnt leave until 10:45.. Seether an Shinedown were the best. Micheal b terry got kicked out n arrested for being drunk n disorderly. they fought each other. i had to carry michael around the crowd to find terry n he was steppin all over my heels n crap. then terry got in trouble n they both got shot with tazer guns. Me n rachel n lindsey went to the front where the moshpit was n me n ray got kicked in the head a couple of times n ray got knocked out n i had 2 help her outta there. I got left n was lookin 4 everyone for about an hour an a half. my bro got kicked out to. he was crowd surfin an the cops got him n kicked him out. he walked around b'ham for 20 mins lookin 4 where we parked. we didnt know he got kicked out until my mom got there n she had to take us home cuz ray collasped from exsaustion. We had grocery store feet. they look nasty. Then heidi terrys sister left jessica [rachels sister] and she had to walk 20 blocks just to find a phone n got left in b'ham. but overall we had a good time. I got ate up by fire ants which i am allergic too. I hate how i feel today cuz my head hurts really badly n it wont stop ponding, and my feet feel like they are gonna fall off. but yea i would do it all over again cuz i had lots of fun but neways i g2g holla

Wuts up everyone... Im soo tired i got back yesterday from Orlando at 5 in the morning. My legs n everything hurt from walking around soo much. We went to Bucsh Gardens, Universal Studios, and Islands of Adventures. The best was Bucsh Gardens because it was a big safari. It had all kinds of animals an rides. I didnt ride any roller coasters though[im scaredd of heights]. Lauren, Nicole, and I rode the sky line the most cause Lauren yelled at everyone... it was funny. We went and saw this 4-d movie called the haunted lighthouse and it shot water at you and fake rats came under ur seats and touched ur feet we freaked out. It was cool though. At universal we rode more rides... like jaws ans E.T. and the woody woodpecker kiddy roller coaster. It was Ok. I think the very best rides were at islands of adventures though cause they had the spiderman and the dudley doright rip saw falls. we got soaking wet on that ride. The drop at the end was sooo steep that when you went down it u couldnt breathe to scream. We were so mad though because of what we saw on a sign. taking back Sunday was going to play right after we left. But anyways tomorrow is goin 2 sux because i got to get my tonsils and adnoids out. I got told it was going to hurt really bad. I will be out of school for two weeks though. Nikki is gonna be over here EvErDaY and help me out around the house n take care of me.... i luv u Nikki!! well neways i g2g i'll holla l8er...
